
v0.04 2012.05.16
  Moved to github
  ExtUtils::MakeMaker instead of Module::Build
  Clean up the tests
  Add version number to all the modules


v0.03 2006.09.22
  New tubes:
  - grep

  Change the run mode, 
  my $p = Pipe->cat("file");        # returns a Pipe object
  $p->run;   # executes the pipe.

  my $p = Pipe->cat("file")->run;   # also works

